The slide dye to outage was only in the last couple of hours...main blow today was the whistle blower incidentExpect that there will be a prolonged dip before recovery and long term damage to advertiser trust
Tech / Facebook :: Facebook servers are out but European investigation is the longer term risk

Facebook / IG / Whatsapp outage appears to be at the DNS level i.e the system resolving website domain names to IP addresses. This is  from a technical standpoint an uncomplicated cause of outage despite the massive impact at global scale
While long term investors may be tempted to buy the glitch  a more pertinent issue announced 2 hours ago may prove to be the bigger issue facing facebook
Along with claims (unverified) of 1.5b personal account information being sold on the dark web as of Sept 2021https://betanews.com/2021/09/24/clubhouse-facebook-records-sale-dark-web/
Tech / Facebook ::The risk is biased towards increased regulatory risk / higher discount in the mid/long run
